  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC066">
  <l>poruṇmai cuṭṭal viyaṅkoḷ varutal</l>
	<l>viṉainilai yuraittal viṉāviṟ kēṟṟal</l>
	<l>paṇpukoḷa varutal peyarkoḷa varutaleṉ</l>
	<l>ṟaṉṟi yaṉaittum peyarppaya ṉilaiyē.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
