  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n68/mode/1up">65</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n70/mode/1up">67</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. poruṇmaicuṭṭal-āvuṇṭu eṉpatu. viyaṅkoḷvarutal-ācelka eṉpatu. viṉainilaiyuraittal-ākiṭantatu eṉpatu. viṉāviṟkēṟṟal-aḵtiyātu, aḵtevaṉ eṉa viṉāccolloṭu toṭartal. paṇpukoḷavarutal-ākaritu eṉpatu. taṉṉiṉamuṭitta leṉpataṉāṉ āvillai, āvalla eṉṉun toṭakkattuk kuṇapporuḷavallā viṉaikkuṟippoṭu toṭartaluṅ koḷka. peyarkoḷavarutal-āpala eṉpatu. aṉṟi yaṉaittum peyarppayaṉilaiyēyeṉpatu avvāṟum peyarvēṟṟumaip payaṉilaiyām. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>muṭikkuñcoṟporuḷ attoṭarmoḻikkup payaṉākaliṟ payaṉilaiyeṉṟār.</p>
<p>uṇṭeṉpatu paṇpumutalāyiṉa cuṭṭātu uṇmaiyē cuṭṭaliṉ, vēṟukūṟiṉār. poypporuḷiṉ meypporuṭku vēṟṟumai uṇmaiyākaliṉ, avvuṇmaiyaip poruṇmaiyeṉṟār.</p>
<p>viyaṅkoḷvarutal viṉainilaiyuraittaṟkaṇṇum, viṉāviṟkēṟṟal peyarkoḷavarutaṟkaṇṇum, viṉaikkuṟippāyavaḻip paṇpukoḷa varutaṟkaṇṇum aṭaṅkumāyiṉum, viṉaiyum peyarum paṇpum muṭikkuñcollā talēyaṉṟi muṭikkappaṭuñcollātalumuṭaiya, viyaṅkōḷum viṉāvum muṭikkuñcollāyallatu nillāmaiyiṉ, avvēṟupāṭaṟivittaṟku vēṟu kūṟiṉāreṉpatu.</p>
<p>"peyartōṉṟunilai" eṉpataṉāṉum, aṉṟi yaṉaittum peyarppaya ṉilaiyē eṉpataṉāṉum, peyar tōṉṟiya tuṇaiyāy niṉṟu payaṉilaittātal eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyatilakkaṇameṉpatu peṟṟām.</p>
<p>āpala eṉpuḻip palaveṉpataṟkup payaṉilai yāteṉiṉ;- atu payaṉilaiyāy āveṉpataṉai muṭittaṟkuvantatākaliṉ, tāṉ piṟitorcoṉṉōkkātu āveṉpataṉoṭu toṭarntu ataṉai muṭittamaintu māṟumeṉpatu. aḵtēl, payaṉilaikoḷḷātatu eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyāmā ṟeṉṉaiyeṉiṉ:- urupēṟṟal peyarkkilakkaṇamāyiṉum urupēlātavaḻiyum peyarāmāṟupōla, eḻuvāyvēṟṟumai payaṉilai koḷḷātavaḻiyum eḻuvāy vēṟṟumaiyē yāmeṉpatu. ilakkiyameṅkuñ cellātaṉa ilakkaṇa māmāṟeṉṉaiyeṉiṉ:- āṇṭilakkaṇamāvaṉa urupēṟṟaṟkēṟṟa taṉmaiyum payaṉilaiyum payaṉilai kōṭaṟkēṟṟa taṉmaiyumākaliṉ, attaṉmai ellāvaṟṟiṟku muṇmaiyiṉ ilakkaṇamāmeṉpatu.</p>
<p>akaraccuṭṭu aṉṟiyeṉavīṟu tirintu niṉṟatu. aṉṟiyaṉaittum peyarppayaṉilaiyeṉavē, payaṉilaikōṭal peyarkkilakkaṇameṉpatūum peṟṟām.	(5)</p>
    </body>
